Malcolm Macarthur seeks refuge in the home of his friend Patrick Connolly. He is driven around in a State car. But gardaí have now established the connection with the Attorney General and move in to arrest him. This is episode five of seven. You can find the other episodes here. GUBU is researched, reported and narrated by Harry McGee and edited by Enda O’Dowd. Sound mix by JJ Vernon. Title music by Orakhal. Graphics by Paul Scott.